<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<style>
body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #faf9f7; color: #2c3e2d; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
.wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
.header { background: #4a7c59; padding: 32px 40px; text-align: center; }
.header h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0; }
.header p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 0.9rem; }
.body { padding: 40px; }
.body h2 { color: #4a7c59; margin-top: 0; }
.detail-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e6e1; font-size: 0.95rem; }
.detail-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.detail-label { color: #6b7768; }
.badge-paid { display: inline-block; background: #4a7c59; color: #fff; padding: 4px 12px; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; }
.success-box { background: #f0f7f2; border-left: 3px solid #4a7c59; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 1rem 1.25rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #2c3e2d; }
.footer { background: #f5f3ef; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #6b7768; }
.footer a { color: #7d8c6f; text-decoration: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Les patounes du glazik</h1>
        <p>Petsitting &amp; Naturopathie animalière</p>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
        <h2>Bonjour {{ member.firstName }},</h2>

        <div class="success-box">
            Votre paiement a bien été reçu. Merci !
        </div>

        <h3 style="color:#4a7c59;margin-top:1.5rem;">Détails de la facture</h3>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Numéro</span>
            <span>{{ invoice.number }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Service</span>
            <span>{{ invoice.booking.serviceType.label() }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Montant réglé</span>
            <span><strong>{{ invoice.amount|number_format(2, ',', ' ') }} €</strong></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Date de paiement</span>
            <span>{{ invoice.paidAt|date('d/m/Y à H:i') }}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-row">
            <span class="detail-label">Statut</span>
            <span class="badge-paid">Payée</span>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-top:1.5rem;font-size:0.9rem;color:#6b7768;">
            Votre facture PDF est disponible depuis votre espace client. Pour toute question, contactez Sophie : <a href="tel:+33767473251" style="color:#7d8c6f;">07 67 47 32 51</a>.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Les patounes du glazik &mdash; 4 Créach Galliec, 29510 Landudal</p>
        <p><a href="tel:+33767473251">07 67 47 32 51</a> &bull; <a href="mailto:sophielukomski.pro@gmail.com">sophielukomski.pro@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
